===Transitive phrasal verb===
'''to get on''' ('''gets on''', '''getting on''', '''got on''', '''got on''' (''UK''), '''gotten on''' (''US''))
#To [[mount]] (something), [[board]] (especially a vehicle).
#:''Please get on the bus as quickly as possible.''
